#. Tag: para
#: security_vpnserver.xml:542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you use a firewall, start &yast; and open UDP port 1194 as described in "
"<xref linkend=\"st.security.vpn.simplest.vpnserv.yast\"/> of <xref linkend="
"\"pro.security.vpn.simplest.vpnserv\"/> ."
