#. Tag: para
#: security_vpnserver.xml:876
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Repeat <xref linkend=\"st.security.vpn.selectserverca\"/> and <xref linkend="
"\"st.security.vpn.selectsaveca\"/> , but choose the format <guimenu>Only the "
